comments: Tracy is kind but fair. Do your work and participate and you\'ll do well in her class.

I really enjoyed this class because I learned a lot of things through my own research. She encouraged us to choose a topic that we were interested in for our research paper, which made writing it more enjoyable. She\'s an easy grader when it comes to papers, but there are daily quizzes so be warned!
Tracy is a good balance of caring and tough. She cares about her students but makes sure they learn what they need to.
Tracy is a great resource to students and is very fair in her classes.
